@page "/involved"

<PageTitle>Get Involved</PageTitle>

<MudContainer MaxWidth="MaxWidth.Large">
    <MudGrid>
        <MudItem xs="12">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h3" Class="px-4">Get Involved</MudText>
        </MudItem>
        <MudItem xs="12" class="mt-4">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="px-4">
                Silverbridge Harps is always looking for enthusiastic individuals to join our team and contribute to our vibrant community. We believe in the GAA value of volunteerism. Whether you have a passion for coaching, hospitality, or maintenance, we have a place for you. Examples of roles available:
            </MudText>
        </MudItem>
        <MudItem xs="12" class="mt-4">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Class="px-4">Coaching Team</MudText>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="px-4">
                Join our coaching team and help train the next generation of athletes. We are looking for dedicated coaches for various age groups and skill levels.
            </MudText>
        </MudItem>
        <MudItem xs="12" class="mt-4">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Class="px-4">Bar Staff</MudText>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="px-4">
                Our bar staff play a crucial role in creating a welcoming atmosphere for our members and guests. If you have experience in hospitality and enjoy working in a social environment, we would love to have you on our team.
            </MudText>
        </MudItem>
        <MudItem xs="12" class="mt-4">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Class="px-4">Hospitality Team</MudText>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="px-4">
                We are looking for individuals to assist with hospitality during events and matches. This includes serving food and beverages, setting up and cleaning up, and ensuring our guests have a great experience.
            </MudText>
        </MudItem>
        <MudItem xs="12" class="mt-4">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Class="px-4">Pitch Maintenance Team</MudText>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="px-4">
                Help us keep our pitches in top condition. We need volunteers to assist with mowing, lining, and general maintenance to ensure our facilities are always ready for play.
            </MudText>
        </MudItem>
        <MudItem xs="12" class="mt-4">
            <MudText Typo="Typo.h5" Class="px-4">Fundraising Team</MudText>
            <MudText Typo="Typo.body1" Class="px-4">
                Help us keep the club running. We need volunteers to assist with planning activities and helping to raise funds to keep the club running for the community.
            </MudText>
        </MudItem>
        <MudItem xs="12" class="mt-4 mb-12 d-flex justify-content-center">
            <MudButton Variant="Variant.Filled" Color="Color.Primary" Href="/contact">Contact Us to Get Involved</MudButton>
        </MudItem>
    </MudGrid>
</MudContainer>

